Trading


Our highly experienced trading team has worked together and with several members of the investment team for many years. Our trading desk implements the investment team’s trade decisions for all institutional and private client portfolios and adheres to strict procedures to ensure all clients benefit fairly and equally from the investment team’s knowledge and experience.














